net.jxta.impl.content
Class ModuleLifecycleTracker<T extends Module>

java.lang.Object
  net.jxta.impl.content.ModuleLifecycleTracker<T>

public class ModuleLifecycleTracker<T extends Module>
extends Object

Tracks the lifecycle state of an individual Module and encapsulates intialization and startup parameters to allow for de-coupled, asynchronous management of subordinate Modules within the ModuleLifecycleManager.
